<h3>8. Loan Calculator</h3>
<p><strong>Problem:</strong> Borrowers struggle to understand total loan costs.</p>
<p><strong>Tool:</strong> A calculator that inputs loan amount, interest rate, and term. Outputs monthly payments, total interest, and amortization schedule.</p>
